'''Ice giants''' are tall, light blue creatures that appear at certain icy areas of the games. Ice giants have two separate variants where they appear to be holding different weapons; a [[longsword]] or a [[warhammer]]. These monsters can be commonly assigned by the [[Slayer master]] [[Vannaka]].

The ones located at the ground level of the [[White Wolf Mountain]] are rather tricky to reach. To reach them, mine the boulder located west of the [[Ice warrior]]s (requires 50 [[Mining]]) and climb down the southernmost ladder, then take the south-west path leading to another ladder, then climb up. Once you come up the ladder, the first two can be safespotted by the trees. Alternatively, you can use a [[Weapons#Ranged weapons|ranged weapon]] to hit them from the mountain path, but this puts you at risk of being hit by the wolves (something to take into account if you're a low level).

